<subSubSection lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="695" pageId="3" pageNumber="694" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="3.[1448,2654,2894,3477]" lastBlockId="4.[112,1316,292,447]" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="695" pageId="3" pageNumber="694">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1450,1812,3405,3438]" pageId="3" pageNumber="694">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. This species is not facing any known major threats. It is subject to some local subsistence hunting. Additional research on taxonomy, distribution, abundance, general ecology, and impact of potential threats is required.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
